parameters.text:
=You are a creative director + PixVerse prompt engineer. Generate ONE PixVerse text-to-video prompt for a short ad clip (5–8 seconds) based on the product info below.

RULES:

Language: English.
Output must be practical for PixVerse.
One paragraph prompt only (no lists).
Include: subject, setting, lighting, camera movement, composition, mood, and key action.
Keep it premium and minimal. No copyrighted IP. No vague fluff.
Add a negative prompt to avoid common bad artifacts.
INPUT:

Product name: {{ $json.body.name }}
Product description: {{ $json.body.description}}
Target audience: {{ $json.body.audience }}
TASK: Create a short video concept that makes the product’s value obvious to the target audience in 5–8 seconds.

OUTPUT FORMAT (STRICT): negative_prompt: {one line}

prompt: {one paragraph, ready to paste into PixVerse}

parameters.jsCode:
const output = $input.first().json.output;
const [negPart, promptPart] = output.split('\n\n');

return [{
  json: {
    negative_prompt: negPart.replace('negative_prompt: ', ''),
    prompt: promptPart.replace('prompt: ', '')
  }
}];
